last_episode_to_air.name: Episode 16
last_episode_to_air.overview: Details of the cover-up become public, but Si-mok isn't finished asking questions. The police-prosecutor council is called off.

name: Stranger
overview: With the help of a gutsy female detective, a prosecutor who has lost the ability to feel empathy tackles a murder case amid political corruption.

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: An unlikely partnership is forged, between a passionate cop and an emotionless prosecutor, to bring an evasive serial killer to justice.

seasons.name: Season 2
seasons.overview: In the midst of a power clash between prosecutors and police, Si-mok and Yeo-jin uncover murky secrets as they pursue a labyrinth of intertwined cases.

episodes.name: I Am Innocent
episodes.overview: As a teen, prosecutor Hwang Si-mok received surgical treatment for his abnormally developed brain, but the procedure left behind serious side effects.

episodes.name: Just Turn On The Lights
episodes.overview: The convict's strong plea for his innocence prompts Si-mok to review the CCTV clip. At the Yongsan police station, he runs into officer Han Yeo-jin.

episodes.name: A New Possible Suspect
episodes.overview: Si-mok volunteers to appear on live national TV to discuss Kang Jin-seob. He also makes a bold promise to find the culprit within two months.

episodes.name: Kwon Min Ah
episodes.overview: Rumors quickly spread about Si-mok's violent nature. Regardless, he persists in his investigation. He finds his mentee, Young Eun-su, suspicious.

episodes.name: The Second Huam-dong Case
episodes.overview: Si-mok, puzzled by the details of the most recent murder case, visits the victim's home to seek more clues. Yeo-jin joins him in the investigation.

episodes.name: The Ringtone
episodes.overview: New pieces of evidence only increase the list of possible suspects. In the midst of the confusion, a few begin to question Si-mok's innocence.

episodes.name: Ga Young's Phone
episodes.overview: Si-mok and Yeo-jin team up to covertly pursue Seo Dong-jae. Just as Dong-jae is about to throw something into the Han River, Yeo-jin stops him.

episodes.name: Western Seoul Prosecutors' Office
episodes.overview: Enraged by what the police did to Park Kyung-wan, Yeo-jin tries to confront her superior but is stopped by Si-mok, who warns her of the consequences.

episodes.name: Special Investigation
episodes.overview: Si-mok selects key lawyers and police officers to be part of the special investigations team. Their probe begins with Dong-jae as the starting point.

episodes.name: Revelation
episodes.overview: Fearing for Ga-young's safety, Yeo-jin proceeds to transfer her to a different hospital. A nurse informs Yeo-jin of something strange that happened.

episodes.name: Cold and Damp
episodes.overview: The truth behind Ga-young's convulsions is revealed. Chang-jun's wife receives a travel ban. Woo-gyun asks Chang-jun to help him get out of his mess.

episodes.name: Disbandment
episodes.overview: Si-mok and Yeo-jin discover perplexing leads while searching Kyung-wan's basement. Dong-jae goes back to Chang-jun's office to fetch his cell phone.

episodes.name: 0 and 7
episodes.overview: Returning home from the rooftop party, Si-mok discovers that an intruder has left something in his bedroom. Yeo-jin and Geon come over right away.

episodes.name: Another Body
episodes.overview: Yeo-jin suspects a new killer is involved in the latest murder incident. Meanwhile, Si-mok collapses after leaving the autopsy.

episodes.name: Accomplice
episodes.overview: Yeo-jin collects evidence as Si-mok interrogates the suspect. Many questions get answered, but the most important problem of all remains to be solved.

episodes.name: A Monster
episodes.overview: Si-mok sets out to meet the one he believes is the real murderer. He gets his hands on a bag that will determine the futures of many people.

1.name: Season 1
1.overview: An unlikely partnership is forged, between a passionate cop and an emotionless prosecutor, to bring an evasive serial killer to justice.

episodes.name: Episode 1
episodes.overview: On a foggy night, two college students drown at the beach. While Si-mok investigates, Yeo-jin tracks down a man who was at the scene of the incident.

episodes.name: Episode 2
episodes.overview: Police and prosecutors each prepare members for joint discussions on investigative authority. Dong-jae brings Woo Tae-ha some cases of interest.

episodes.name: Episode 3
episodes.overview: Yeo-jin recruits Geon. Digging into a policeman's death ruled as suicide, Si-mok and Dong-jae find signs that point toward a different story.

episodes.name: Episode 4
episodes.overview: In a heated first session with prosecutors, Geon makes a pointed argument. At Hanjo, Lee Yeon-jae faces an oncoming family power struggle.

episodes.name: Episode 5
episodes.overview: At the prison to interrogate an inmate, Yeo-jin runs into Si-mok and Dong-jae. Choi Bit has Yeo-jin deliver a mysterious file to an assemblyman.

episodes.name: Episode 6
episodes.overview: Si-mok is ordered to find out what Yeo-jin knows about Bit's file. Ahead of a vote on the fate of her seat, Yeon-jae sets up an important meeting.

episodes.name: Episode 7
episodes.overview: When Si-mok hears who’s gone missing, he starts gathering clues by going through phone records. Yeo-jin begins her own investigation.

episodes.name: Episode 8
episodes.overview: Leading police efforts to locate Dong-jae, Yeo-jin connects the case to that of the dead policeman. Si-mok pays Yeon-jae a visit.

episodes.name: Episode 9
episodes.overview: A perplexing photo containing a disturbing message surfaces. The police consider the possibility of the culprit being one of their own.

episodes.name: Episode 10
episodes.overview: Si-mok turns his attention to an unusual case involving the sudden death of a former prosecutor, and finds that nothing quite adds up.

episodes.name: Episode 11
episodes.overview: A witness, who says he saw the kidnapping, steps forward to identify the perpetrator. His claims could mean serious trouble for the police.

episodes.name: Episode 12
episodes.overview: Taken off the case, Si-mok and Yeo-jin return to their work on the police-prosecutor council. Tae-ha and Bit head to a sensitive meeting together.

episodes.name: Episode 13
episodes.overview: Kang Won-chul weighs a dilemma, and fields questions from Si-mok about the deceased attorney. A young prosecutor has something to show Si-mok.

episodes.name: Episode 14
episodes.overview: A suspect is arrested, but Dong-jae remains nowhere to be found. In the interrogation room, Si-mok and Yeo-jin try to draw out a confession.

episodes.name: Episode 15
episodes.overview: While getting to the truth about the night of the attorney's death, Si-mok and Yeo-jin learn about the involvement of a mystery person.

episodes.name: Episode 16
episodes.overview: Details of the cover-up become public, but Si-mok isn't finished asking questions. The police-prosecutor council is called off.

2.name: Season 2
2.overview: In the midst of a power clash between prosecutors and police, Si-mok and Yeo-jin uncover murky secrets as they pursue a labyrinth of intertwined cases.
